            "title": "Whole & Broken 💔",
            "content": "In JavaScript, numbers can be:\n\n* **Integers**: Whole numbers (1, 100, -5)\n* **Floats**: Decimals (3.14, 0.5, -2.5)\n\nJS treats them all just as 'Number' type."
